    "body": "There's no mandatory location to place the grpc folder in. The Bazel BUILD file is self-contained, and is relative to itself.\n\nMy personal recommendation however would be to place it in third_party/grpc. Then you can use the target //third_party/grpc:grpc++ as a dependency for your own targets.\n"
